metadata.name: Cloud #1: The Candy Sky Main Character With the Doves.
metadata.description: Clouds by Felt Zine is an experimental 3D clouds-based project of 100 unique artworks exploring the gamification of modern life, nostalgia of physical reality, and video games. Designed by creative director Dev Moore alongside designer Josh Parsons, Fab Foolie, Micah Carroll, and additional production by Mark DigitalHD and Jawn Diego Reyes. Mint, view, and explore view the full collection at feltzine.art.
